Reply with status.

Possible statuses are OK, NOTOK some error occured, NOT_ALLOWED if may not remove key from owner.

Parameters:
req The request with packetID and requestID.
ownerUIN The UIN of the owner of the key, possibly same as in request, 0 if no owner.
